Great location, handy to schools and the sporting precinct.

Description:
Great Central Location - 4 BRs
This residence is in a great location in one of Cobram's older tree lined streets, however surrounded by mainly newer homes & only minutes walk to the main shopping centre, hospital, church's & both primary & secondary schools.
Situated on a generous 1135m2 block, the home is 9 years young & has been constructed using a steel frame. Offers 4 generous sized bedrooms, office, 2 bathrooms (1 with wheel chair access) & 3 toilets, open living plan with northerly aspect. Well designed & equipped kitchen with corner pantry & storeroom off the laundry. Ducted air condit & hydronic heating throughout. 2.1 KW solar panel system, 2 x gas HWS. Double lockup garage & double lockup workshop with power in the rear yard.
Absolute low maintenance & no fuss yard, however a clean canvas for the "green thumb" gardener, if so desired.
Vendors relocating & must be sold.
